<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

.new2012_blue12:hover {COLOR: #ffffff; font-size:12px; TEXT-DECORATION: none;}

</style>
<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

		<td style="text-align:center">

					<td>
					
						
						<table width="100%" class="msgtab" style="background:#eaeaea" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0">

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

								<form name="pageForm" id="pageForm" action="all.do?name=葡萄糖注射液&amp;tableName=TABLE25&amp;formRender=cx&amp;searchcx=葡萄糖&amp;paramter0=&amp;paramter1=&amp;paramter2=" method="post"></form>
								<td width="30%" style="text-align:right;padding-right:45px">跳转 <input name="page" id="page" style="border:1px #7F9EBA solid;height:17px;width:40px" type="text" value="1" /> <input id="dd" style="background:url('./face5/dataimages/cxtiaozhuan.gif');width:29px;height:17px;border:0px" onclick="javascript:jianchao();" type="button" value="" /></td>
							   
							</tr>
						</tbody></table>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody></table>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
</tbody></table>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody></table>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
</tbody></table>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

								<td width="30%" style="text-align:right;padding-right:45px">跳转 <input name="page" id="page" style="border:1px #7F9EBA solid;height:17px;width:40px" type="text" value="1" /> <input id="dd" style="background:url('./face5/dataimages/cxtiaozhuan.gif');width:29px;height:17px;border:0px" onclick="javascript:jianchao();" type="button" value="" /></td>
							   
							</tr>
						</tbody></table>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody></table>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
</tbody></table>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js" type="text/javascript"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

<script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript" src="./face5/js/jquery-sfda.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">
//过滤页码非法数据
	function jianchao(){  
		var value=$("input[id='page']").val();
		var reg = /^\d+$/; 
		
		var re = value.match(reg); 
		//alert(re);   
		if(re){
			var  r = /^\d{0,10}$/;
		   	var reg1=value.match(r);
		 
		   	if(reg1){
		     document.pageForm.submit(); 
		     }
		     else{
		     alert("数字长度过长！")
		     }
			//return true;
		}else{
			alert("请输入正确的页码！");
			//return false;
		
		}
   }

</script></head>

								<form method="post" id="pageForm" name="pageForm" action="all.do?name=葡萄糖注射液&amp;tableName=TABLE25&amp;formRender=cx&amp;searchcx=葡萄糖&amp;paramter0=&amp;paramter1=&amp;paramter2="></form>
								<td width="30%" style="text-align:right;padding-right:45px">跳转 <input id="page" type="text" name="page" value="1" style="border:1px #7F9EBA solid;height:17px;width:40px" /> <input type="button" id="dd" value="" onclick="javascript:jianchao();" style="background:url('./face5/dataimages/cxtiaozhuan.gif');width:29px;height:17px;border:0px" /></td>
							   
							</tr>
						</tbody></table>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody></table>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
</tbody></table>
